<subSubSection id="F6624ACC36A57CD6A1B61B688AA1F114" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="62EFEC0A754D9C05876DA8A791FE13E1" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
<taxonomicName id="10329D63393D1DAA7D49D993C794A03A" authority="Hull, 1937" authorityName="Hull" authorityYear="1937" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Pseudomicrodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pseudomicrodon" order="Diptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pseudomicrodon</taxonomicName>
Hull, 1937a: 24. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="B0228D4E03C8EF2BE0AD8B6252F71AF9" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Microdon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microdon beebei" order="Diptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="beebei">Microdon beebei</taxonomicName>
